OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly schools that scrap   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnativity could face fine   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy's far-right government is seeking
OL,6, to crack down on schools that scrap    
OL,7, Christian nativity scenes in order to  
OL,8, reflect greater religious diversity.   
OL,10,FA draft law introduced on Wednesday    
OL,11,Fseeks to protect the country's         
OL,12,F"cultural roots" by promoting          
OL,13,F"traditional" Christmas and Easter     
OL,14,Fcelebrations.                          
OL,16,FUnder it, principals who choose not to 
OL,17,Fput on nativities could be fined.      
OL,19,FThe move has been widely criticised by 
OL,20,Fopposition parties and school unions.  
